                     <interp inst="t18120513-72-person750" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an apprentice to Mr. Christie. When the prisoner accounted for what money he received, I always put it down in the book. I cannot make a mistake. I call over the names.</p>
               <p>Mr. Gurney. And then he accounts to you for near an hundred names - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18120513-72-person751">
